| Resource | Type | Cost | Notes |
|----------|------|------|-------|
| **Clean Architecture (Robert C. Martin)** | Book | Paid | The foundational book |
| **Domain-Driven Design Quickly (InfoQ)** | E-Book | Free | DDD without the 500-page commitment |
| **Milan Jovanovic (YouTube + Newsletter)** | Video/Blog | Free | Best .NET-specific clean architecture content |
| **codewithmukesh.com** | Blog | Free | Clean Architecture in ASP.NET Core series |
